data.description: Incredible, one of a kind home with beautiful mountain and city views. Have the privacy of 10+ acres yet be only 5 minutes to stores and restaurants. This home features 6 bedrooms, 4 bathrooms, 5789 SF, large open kitchen perfect for entertaining, and beautiful wood work throughout. There are also 4 fireplaces, a wine cellar, large deck, hot tub, new furnace, and a new roof. Located in a desirable neighborhood with access to National Forest. Places like this don't become available often. Come see it today! Motivated seller willing to look at all offers.
